Slovenian Banks Can Still Count on ECB Financing, NLB Chief Says

-- B y   B o r i s   C e r n i
-- 
2011-09-29T12:04:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-29/slovenian-banks-can-still-count-on-ecb-financing-nlb-chief-says.html
Slovenian banks can still count on
the  European Central Bank  for financing in case they run into
liquidity problems, Bozo Jasovic, chief executive officer of
Nova Ljubljanska Banka d.d., told a business forum in
Portoroz, Slovenia today.  “This, of course, isn’t a long-term solution,” he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Boris Cerni in Ljubljana at 
 bcerni@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Douglas Lytle at 
 dlytle@bloomberg.net  